## Naming conventions

| Artifact | Convention |
|----------|-----------|
| DB entity type | `DB_Asset` |
| DB def | `DBDef_Assets` |
| Database def type | `DatabaseDef_Assets` |
| Backend module | `ModuleBE_FileUpload` |
| Frontend upload/download module | `ModuleFE_FileUpload` |
| Frontend CRUD module | `ModuleFE_Assets` |
| Backend module pack | `ModulePackBE_FileUpload` |
| Frontend module pack | `ModulePackFE_FileUpload` |
| API type | `API_FileUpload` |
| API def constant | `ApiDef_FileUpload` |
| Default UI component | `TransferBubble` |
| Dispatcher interface | `OnFileTransferStateChanged` |
| Transfer state type | `FileTransferState` |
| Direction type | `TransferDirection` |

