## Forbidden patterns

- **Do not call `confirmUpload` without a prior `requestUpload`** — the asset must exist in `pending` status.
- **Do not upload without registering a validator** — `requestUpload` will throw if no validator matches the key.
- **Do not rely on exception messages for validation errors** — use `ConfirmUploadResponse.error` (the structured field).
- **Do not set inline styles on `TransferBubble`** — override via SCSS custom properties and class selectors only.
- **Do not import `StorageAdapter_GCS` in consuming packages** — it is an internal implementation. Use `ModuleBE_FileUpload.setStorageAdapter()` if swapping.
